987): 376-7[6] Darpo B "Spectrum of drugs prolonging QT interval and the incidence of torsades de pointes." Eur Heart J Suppl 3(Suppl K) (2001): K70-80[7] Cerner Multum, Inc. "UK Summary of Product Characteristics." O 0', 1767365205);
